c: 6
v: 31
t: "Ntankeka baramaze gushikirwa n’uruhombo bamwe bahakanye yuko batazohura n’Imana yabo kugeza aho bazoshikirwa giturumbuka nico gihe, baciye bavuga bati:- oh! amaganya yacu ari hejuru yabimwe twanegura, nabo bazokwikorera amatu yabo kumigongo yabo, rero nimurabe namwe ayo mabi bikoreye"